{"tid":704453,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"屌那公 冇出街食飯一排 都唔知原來E家出面啲米價咁撚搶錢","createTime":"2018-06-16T13:17:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-25T13:02:31.000Z","uid":120980,"like":34,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"a49d9eb6d843ee7a31ab9541684e827f21ccf901","tid":704453,"uid":120980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T13:17:27.000Z","msg":"對上一次食大檸樂嘅一哥焗豬都係$41<br />\n<br />\n冚家剷原來家下已經跳錶跳到去$47<br />\n<br />\n真係平均一個月加一兩蚊咁滯<br />\n<br />\n咁樣跳法 唔敢想像10年後嘅米價 加埋通貨膨脹 食一碟焗豬洗唔洗過百<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有以往貪平 食茶記果啲碟頭飯每碟都係$34至$35<br />\n<br />\n家下已經又係要4字頭<br />\n<br />\n加價都算 加價之餘啲份量仲要縮晒水<br />\n<br />\n唔學識煮飯未來真係搵多多都唔夠自己食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3683264bbde8458a4ead1cb32ad9be63ef868e80","tid":704453,"uid":106778,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T13:22:00.000Z","msg":"狗屎垃圾都賣4字頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88564544bc0fb1b5b51cbc32c3783327d78bd669","tid":704453,"uid":58316,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T14:13:44.000Z","msg":"$20 交租<br />\n$10 廣告<br />\n$5 人工<br />\n$5 燈油火蠟<br />\n$7 焗豬扒飯"},{"pid":"098d9140c882a583a88c33976631500f68e26b99","tid":704453,"uid":120980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3683264bbde8458a4ead1cb32ad9be63ef868e80","tid":704453,"uid":106778,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T13:22:00.000Z","msg":"狗屎垃圾都賣4字頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T14:38:07.000Z","msg":"好撚驚2019年就要5字頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84cf5c041f31cb7e72febc4d9099d3f3e46d1a37","tid":704453,"uid":142433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"098d9140c882a583a88c33976631500f68e26b99","tid":704453,"uid":120980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3683264bbde8458a4ea